frames.caption: A giant, surreal banana sculpture dominates a bustling urban plaza, attracting numerous visitors. People are seen walking around and climbing the banana, creating a lively and whimsical atmosphere. The scene is set against a backdrop of modern skyscrapers under a clear blue sky.
